  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sharing of experience in the field of climate change</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Zdie&#x13E;anie sk&#xFA;senost&#xED; v oblasti zmeny kl&#xED;my</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;On September 29 - October 4, 2019, a 4-member delegation from Serbia visited Slovakia. The primary objective of the study visit was to increase the expertise and reinforce the capacity of the Serbian Ministry of Environmental Protection&#xA0;in the field of climate change, but also to exchange experiences and examples of best practice in mitigation and adaptation (meeting EU commitments, Paris Agreement commitments, UNFCCC commitments and related reporting obligations). The participants of the visit were acquainted with the setting of the Slovak legislative framework in this area. The study visit also created conditions for establishing longer-term cooperation of the Slovak Ministry of Environment with Serbia, as well as with the Western Balkans region.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;V d&#x148;och 29. septembra &#x2013; 4. okt&#xF3;bra 2019 nav&#x161;t&#xED;vila Slovensko 4-&#x10D;lenn&#xE1; deleg&#xE1;cia zo Srbska.&#xA0;Prim&#xE1;rnym cie&#x13E;om &#x161;tudijnej n&#xE1;v&#x161;tevy bolo zv&#xFD;&#x161;enie odbornosti a posilnenie kapac&#xED;t srbsk&#xE9;ho M&#x17D;P v oblasti zmeny kl&#xED;my, ale aj v&#xFD;mena sk&#xFA;senost&#xED; a pr&#xED;klady osved&#x10D;en&#xFD;ch postupov v oblasti mitig&#xE1;cie i adapt&#xE1;cie (plnenie z&#xE1;v&#xE4;zkov E&#xDA;, Par&#xED;&#x17E;skej dohody, R&#xE1;mcov&#xE9;ho dohovoru OSN o zmene kl&#xED;my UNFCCC). &#xDA;&#x10D;astn&#xED;&#x10D;ky n&#xE1;v&#x161;tevy boli obozn&#xE1;men&#xE9; s nastaven&#xED;m slovensk&#xE9;ho legislat&#xED;vneho r&#xE1;mca v tejto oblasti. &#x160;tudijn&#xE1; n&#xE1;v&#x161;teva taktie&#x17E; vytvorila podmienky pre nadviazanie dlhodobej&#x161;ej spolupr&#xE1;ce M&#x17D;P SR so Srbskom, ako aj &#x161;ir&#x161;ie s regi&#xF3;nom Z&#xE1;padn&#xE9;ho Balk&#xE1;nu v oblasti &#x17E;ivotn&#xE9;ho prostredia.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
